        <num>18-2-57</num>
        <content>
          <p>When the assignment is attacked as fraudulent or void for any reason, it shall not be necessary to show fraud or collusion or notice thereof in the assignee in order to render the assignment void.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1894, p. 90, ยง 15; Civil Code 1895, ยง 2712; Civil Code 1910, ยง 3245; Code 1933, ยง 28-316.)</p>
